          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>Our Wolf stove repair services address issues such as:</p>
            <ul>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Burners not igniting or uneven flames</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Oven not reaching or holding temperature</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Inconsistent baking or roasting results</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Knobs or touch controls unresponsive</strong></li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Error codes</strong> like E20, E30, or E50</li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-2 no-bullet pl-0" ><Icon icon="check" class="icon-class" /><strong>Convection fan not running</strong></li>
