        </div>

        <div class="content-container">
          <div class="full-width-content">
            <p>Our advice is based on your stove's age, condition, and needs:</p>
            <ul style="margin-bottom: 20px;">
              <li><strong>Repair</strong> – If the unit is under 20 years old and in otherwise excellent shape</li>
